//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Poseidon.jpg?v=1749598655", "All Images": ["https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Poseidon.jpg?v=1749598655", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Geranium.jpg?v=1749598655", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Siren.jpg?v=1749598655", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Sundown.jpg?v=1749598655", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem.jpg?v=1749598655", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Downstem.jpg?v=1749598655", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Universal-Downstem.jpg?v=1749598655", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Onyx.jpg?v=1749598655"], "Specs": "Active, Duoplane, Loc4, Metal, Water Pipe Downstems, Water Pipe Joint Angle: 90\u00b0, Water Pipe Joint Gender: Female, Water Pipe Joint Gender: Male, Water Pipe Joint Size: 14Mm, Water Pipe Joint Size: 18Mm", "Description": "<div class=\"original-desc\"><p>Whether you\u00e2\u20ac\u2122re tired of trying to measure broken downstems, or perhaps prefer different water levels in your bong, the\u00c2\u00a0Invincipole\u00c2\u00a0Indestructible Universal Downstem\u00c2\u00a0is here to save the day! This unique adjustable downstem from Invincibowl can extend anywhere from 3\u00e2\u20ac\u009d to 5 3/4\u00e2\u20ac\u009d inches in length and is compatible with any 14mm and 18mm joint beaker bong or straight-based water pipe with a 45\u00b0 joint angle.\u00c2\u00a0This downstem is indestructible\u00c2\u00a0and is constructed with aluminum, so you\u00e2\u20ac\u2122ll never have to replace your downstem again. The Invincipole Universal\u00c2\u00a0Downstem features a diffuser that expertly filters your smoke through water for the smoothest hits.</p> <p><img alt=\\\"Invincipole Indestructible Universal Downstem\\\" src=\\\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2745/9564/files/Invincipole_Indestructible_Universal_Downstem_480x480_b71ae13b-7943-45ee-8e75-f0fc70823d1f.jpg?v=1700549810\\\"></p> <h3><em><strong>Get Connected:</strong></em></h3> <p>Invincipole Indestructible Universal Downstem<br>Aerospace-Grade Aluminum Body<br>Adjustable 3-5 3/4\u00e2\u20ac\u009d inch Length<br>Diffuser Downstem<br>Easy to Clean<br data-mce-fragment=\\\"1\\\">Choice of Colors<br>Replacement Water Pipe\u00c2\u00a0Downstem<br>Holds 14mm Male Bowls/Accessories<br>Fits Inside 14mm &amp; 18mm Female Joints<br></p></div>", "Variants": [{"name": "Onyx (Black)", "sku": "IP14-BLK-I", "wholesale": 25.0, "price": 49.99, "msrp": "71.99", "image": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem.jpg?v=1749598655", "stock": 10}, {"name": "Poseidon (Blue)", "sku": "IP14-BLU-I", "wholesale": 25.0, "price": 49.99, "msrp": "68.99", "image": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Poseidon.jpg?v=1749598655", "stock": 9}, {"name": "Siren (Red)", "sku": "IP14-RED-I", "wholesale": 25.0, "price": 49.99, "msrp": "68.99", "image": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Siren.jpg?v=1749598655", "stock": 7}, {"name": "Sundown (Orange)", "sku": "IP14-ORG-I", "wholesale": 25.0, "price": 49.99, "msrp": "71.99", "image": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincipole-Indestructible-Universal-Downstem-Sundown.jpg?v=1749598655", "stock": 1}], "isAuditorChoice": false, "rating": 4.9, "reviews": 34}, {"Brand": "Invincibowl", "Category": "Spoon", "Product Name": "Invincibowl Indestructible Replacement Bowl - 14mm Male", "Base Price": 34.99, "Primary Image": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincibowl_Black_Vert.jpg?v=1749598643", "All Images": ["https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincibowl_Black_Vert.jpg?v=1749598643", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincibowl_Blue_Vert.jpg?v=1749598643", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincibowl_Red_Vert.jpg?v=1749598643", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincibowl_Pink_Vert.jpg?v=1749598643", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/2780/5886/files/Invincibowl_Orange_Vert.jpg?v=1749598643"], "Specs": "Active, Duoplane, Loc4, Metal, Water Pipe Bowl Pieces, Water Pipe Joint Angle: 90\u00b0, Water Pipe Joint Gender: Male, Water Pipe Joint Size: 14Mm", "Description": "<div class=\"original-desc\"><p>The Invincibowl is the perfect\u00c2\u00a0accessory for smokers who want a t<meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\">ruly indestructible bowl to accent their favorite bong. This shatterproof bowl piece is made from aerospace-grade aluminum\u00c2\u00a0with a\u00c2\u00a0304 surgical stainless steel screen, making it incredibly durable. The Secure-screen technology allows you to invert the device, discarding ash without dropping the screen, while the high-flow screen ensures an even burn. The flat bottom design prevents waste accumulation, and the insulated grip guard protects against thermal damage. Each Invincibowl package includes two spare screens, making it the perfect choice for any smoker.<br></p> <p><img alt=\\\"Invincibowl 14mm Indestructible Replacement Bowl\\\" src=\\\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2745/9564/files/Invincibowl-Indestructible-Replacement-Bowl_480x480_153c0bbc-eeee-41b9-ab90-6abbf22a3f97.jpg?v=1700549791\\\"></p> <p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.4em;\\\"><em><strong>Get Connected:</strong></em></span><br></p> <p>Compatible with Dry Herbs \u00f0\u0178\u0152\u00bf<br>Invincibowl 14mm Indestruct